  "text": "These additional functions include encapsidation or serving as a target of silencing [CITATION_1] . In TEV, it has been shown that certain synonymous mutations had deleterious effect on the virus multiplication [CITATION_2] , and the present study provides a striking example of nonneutrality of synonymous mutations with the two lineages which lost the capacity to produce systemic infection on certain hosts and only carry synonymous mutations.",
